<br>
Does the Magician have epic? If so then their pet damage more than doubles<br>
<br>
Do they have Shield of auras? Forget about Boots of bladecalling, a mage with shield of auras is an insane damage machine.  Im willing to bet its one of the all around better caster right clicks in the game, perhaps other casters need an item with such magnitude<br>
<br>
Also, I have to disagree with Grimstaff about magician class AA <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  They arent &quot;neat&quot; or &quot;good&quot; hehe..They're basically completely worthless from mine and many other magicians perspectives.  Since on paper they seem good, but in reality do not do what they should<br>
<br>
Anyway the wizard chart was interesting to read <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Ive come under the impression that Wizards are the masters of doing quick damage against *any* mob (Except tunare since she was forgotten in the resist change or something), but do not get high damage against a particular mob<br>
<br>
While mages are masters of sustained damage, and especially high damage against level 55 and under mobs due to pet hitting much better.. and of course if the mage has shield of auras their contribution is substaintally improved<br>
<br>
I have a lot of wizard friends and my issue with wizards is pre60.  Yes I'm not a wizard, but I think every class deserves balance <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  and Im rather distressed at the 1-59 collection of wizard spells, seems odd to me that only at 60 do they recieve damaging spells (Sorta along the line with clerics who only recieve their best spells at 59-60, ignoring complete heal) While other classes, especially druids, mages and enchanters recieve their top spells much earlier and their power progression is much more steady up to 60.. Rather than recieving jack at 51-59 and then everything at 60 heh<br>
<br>
Ylaine<br>
